00:07:36.570 --> 00:07:43.450
But we'll continue to be, you know, always stay alert to competition, and, you know,

00:07:43.450 --> 00:07:48.330
they're going to have to work very hard to catch us, we're quite formidable ourselves,

00:07:48.330 --> 00:07:53.370
And we worked pretty hard for the customers and where, you know, the Nvidia employees

00:07:53.370 --> 00:07:54.610
