00:09:02.850 --> 00:09:08.170
in hardware and software upstream in our supply chain downstream through our data

00:09:08.170 --> 00:09:15.170
centers and so there's so many partners that we work with is really a privilege for us to

00:09:15.170 --> 00:09:18.450
