00:09:18.450 --> 00:09:24.610
Ultimately, Maria, this is the largest manufacturing industry in the world.

00:09:24.610 --> 00:09:26.490
That I think is certain now.

00:09:26.490 --> 00:09:33.450
The production of intelligence will be much, much larger than the production of energy,

00:09:33.450 --> 00:09:36.610
