What's the strategy long-term?

00:10:40.290 --> 00:10:43.930
The strategy is to help build out this five-layer cake.

00:10:43.930 --> 00:10:45.890
And this five-layer cake represents

00:10:45.890 --> 00:10:48.490
a brand new industry called AI.

00:10:48.490 --> 00:10:51.970
It includes energy all the way to applications on top.

00:10:51.970 --> 00:10:56.170
And we look across this ecosystem

00:10:56.170 --> 00:10:57.570
