he said that Corning is gonna build 10 times

00:11:23.770 --> 00:11:26.930
as much fiber optics technology,

00:11:26.930 --> 00:11:31.610
fiber optics capability in the United States than previously because of the partnership

00:11:31.610 --> 00:11:32.770
